Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Admission process, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uniform, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,School regulations, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cockpit regulations, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Aerial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did an application for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arriving at Front Sector 73,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asticassia School of Technology, in five minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ship will now enter a docking course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-They'll die!{\i0}\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Someone is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Someone is outside!{\i0}\N-Rescue team, alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A person is in need of rescue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Prepare for extravehicular activity.{\i0}\N-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Please confirm victim's status.{\i0}\N-It should be over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are there any signs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of collision with debris?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move forward, you gain two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rescue to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they intend to leave the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attention mobile suit pilot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're opening the exit hatch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay put until then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you spot someone{\i0}\N{\i1}in need of rescue, let us know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll respond immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost out of oxygen. Beginning rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Can you--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd almost made my escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you, it's all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll take responsibility for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta Mercury?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to observe the drills, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nika Nanaura,\Na second-year student in Mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any questions, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, M...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank y...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank y-you verr...\N-Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've never...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,been to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a school before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is it true you're from Mercury?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do people live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your major?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the Piloting department...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-That makes you one of the elite!\N-What did you transfer here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,told me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So did she also tell you\Nto wear that old-fashioned hair band?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine Rembran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare immediately to join the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll take...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll help you with your escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just tell me what I should do!\N-It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the girl who got in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Responsibility?\N-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-This isn't the place...\N-Responsibility, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not let her take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to run away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-To Earth.\N-Class is in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No more chatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A red Dilanza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Guel Jeturk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apologies for interrupting your drills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is an official duel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}approved by the Dueling Committee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Shaddiq Zenelli, will be the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ask that no one interfere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A duel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That way is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way.\N-Are they coming toward us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Do you want to get hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How Guel Jeturk fights his duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and the company
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will be mine before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is still in session, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The bastard down there laughed at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling me a man with a runaway bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules say that when you lose,\Nyou apologize like a groveling worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to see how he does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,for saving me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ms. Miorine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-About your fiance--\N-Stop. I never agreed to any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,just decided on his own that you're engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was a duel.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At our school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the students settle\Nimportant matters through duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, authority, apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even marriage partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My lousy father designed it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeturk Heavy Machinery,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Peil Technologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Grassley Defense Systems...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These three are the Benerit Group's\Nhighest earners for this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the Parneo Company has recorded a loss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for three consecutive periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our group has no need\Nfor companies in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am hereby suspending their access\Nto the group's finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a minute, President Delling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-If that happens, we'll go bank--{\i0}\N-Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Their financial documents indicate\Nthere is potential for recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They've had their chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I'm interested in is results.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've assigned two agents\Nto keep watch on Mistress Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to meet them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know better than to waste my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tomato, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tomato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you Mercurians eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have tomato flavoring, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just bite into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all tomatoes taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-She made a tomato?\N-That specific breed, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,sent me here to study, so that I could
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,make Mercury a more prosperous planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So your mother is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand me your student notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know the way back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I've given you the school map app,\Nscram and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing farmer again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All this pretending you're on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what's it good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Guel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just barge in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I came up with a bright idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you're gonna live\Nwith us at Jeturk House.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have any more\Nescape attempts, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never agreed to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your father who made the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we always have to follow\Nwhat our parents decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you daddy's little lap dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how clumsy, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Better watch yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We have to... we have to stop--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to stop my brother, do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She needs h...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been too lenient with you, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As your future husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to teach you some discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to shut your mouth\Nand give yourself over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Didn't your mother ever teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't act like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A pushy suitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the heir to one of\Nthe three branches of the Benerit Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the head of the Dueling Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reigning Holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The school's number one pilot,\Nas chosen through duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's wrong is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell Ms. Miorine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,right and wrong are decided through duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you like to duel me yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I will duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! This has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose, you'll have to leave the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right.\N-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the carrier to Gate No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Load it with spare packs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The carrier is now moving to Gate No.2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare packages are loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gonna be a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With Mr. Guel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's he against?\N-A transfer student, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Passage to tactical testing sector.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No obstacles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takeoff granted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If Delling dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my son Guel's engagement will be secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to act before the results\Nof these silly "duels" are nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the detonation\Nfor ten minutes after launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Delling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,our long friendship ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Environmental setting data {\i0}\N{\i1}for tactical testing sector received.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coriolis correction, stable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bioinfo, identification complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Permet link, satisfactory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,KP001, Guel Jeturk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilanza, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to watch, Elan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why accept a duel{\i0}\N{\i1}from that country bumpkin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it quick for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the future ace of Dominicus, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is. The Mercurian girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Tricolor means a three-colored flag,\N-She's got a flashy one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-especially the national emblem of old France.\N-I don't see a logo. Could it be handmade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Arriving at the designated coordinates.\N-{\i1}With mutual consent by both parties,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we will now begin the duel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, victory will go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to the first one to break the blade antenna\Nof their opponent's mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both parties, face off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Isn't that the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was the transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Ms. Miorine board Aerial?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of people making decisions for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Impudent girl. Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you firsthand\Nthat you're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you approve the change in duel opponent?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is never decided by\Nmobile suit performance alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor by the skill of the pilot, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-The result itself is the only truth!\N-The result itself is the only truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix release!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons. Where are the weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think any amateur\Ncould handle a mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,let me do as I please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll decide for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess of Management Strategy\Nhas no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take a good look at yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're nothing more than a trophy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An alert?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who the hell are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exceeding speed limit.　　{\i0}\N{\i1}Please decrease speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it showing your name, Nika?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give it back!\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you, this has nothing to do with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then fight in your own mobile suit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Don't be so stingy!{\i0}\N-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-It's just another mobile suit!{\i0}\N-A falling-out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aerial isn't just another one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were raised together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let me fulfill\Nmy responsibility by winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial and I will never
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,lose to the likes of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"The likes of him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddiq, I'm changing opponents again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him the go ahead, Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll correct your ignorance,\Nyou country bumpkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you run, you gain one,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"but if you move forward, you gain two."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When you run, you gain one by not losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you move forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you win or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there are two things you gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience and pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She blocked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of mobile suit is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,GUND-ARM...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What... What the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jeturk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-A last-minute intervention?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your son was defeated in a duel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you killed President Delling now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Guel won't be Mistress Miorine's fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the opponent? Grassley?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Peil?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta Mercury...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This attire is the emblem of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The emblem of the Holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also the emblem of my fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I? Those are the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Mercury is rather conservative.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing is commonplace here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, my groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NMobile Suit Gundam: The Witch from Mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Cursed Mobile Suit."{\i0}
